Class IloCplex.VariableSelect

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.VariableSelect
  • Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.VariableSelect
extends java.lang.Object
    Enumeration of possible values for the IloCplex.IntParam.VarSel parameter.

    Use these values with the method IloCplex.setParam(IloCplex.IntParam.VarSel, value).
